String.string: Do you have any idea what you've just done?
Kill {@linkcreature:30#140#venomous tentacullars} in {@Rgn:30006$$Brightleaf Glade} and get their poison.
Deliver the poison to the {@linkcreature:230#1018#veteran itinerant miner}.
Show the poison to the {@linkcreature:230#1017$$novice itinerant miner}, a coworker of the {@linkcreature:230#1018$$veteran itinerant miner}.
"How do I get into these things?"
Go tell {@linkcreature:230#1065$$Libinienn} what happened to the {@linkcreature:230#1018#veteran itinerant miner}.
